# Polar H10 Real-Time Heart Rate Monitor

This project connects to a Polar H10 heart rate monitor via Bluetooth and displays real-time heart rate data using Python.

## Setup

1. **Install Python** from [python.org](https://www.python.org/).
2. **Install required packages**:
    ```sh
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    ```

## Usage

Run the `polar_h10_realtime.py` script:
